metadata.name: blinded
metadata.description:
I see beyond my eyes
I feel beneath my skin
I fight all these invisible wars
And this makes me who i am
I am more than that i once was
They rip me apart into ions
And i rebuild myself all over again
I add parts to myself, modify myself
To shield myself, to resist all this evil
After each attempt,
I become more than what i was
Am i better now? I do not know.
But i am scarred and stronger
I am blinded by my reality
I am a mess, floating endlessly
In this incomprehensible world.
Beyond the intergalactic space
On a negligible planet, i stay
I mark my land here
And i will make myself be known
Each battle invigorates me
So I stay immersed in this world
Seeking out for more
